name: My Little Pony Transformer
description:
This is a body paint cosplay I produced that went viral back in 2014. Decided to do a mashup of My Little Pony and Transformers as I lived less than a mile from Hasbro back then. Watch the video to see us crash the headquarters for a guerrilla photoshoot https://youtu.be/RWNMkazMSvI

model: Megan Tamás
body paint and photography by Roustan (bodypainter.com)
wings, headpiece, and boots by Roustan
